# Copy to .npmrc in your consumer project to install @mahirick/users-and-teams
# from GitHub Packages.
#
# 1. Create a GitHub personal access token with `read:packages` scope.
# 2. Replace YOUR_GITHUB_PAT below with that token (or use the gh-actions
#    secrets mechanism for CI).
# 3. Commit .npmrc but *never* with the real token in it. Use the
#    NPM_TOKEN env var via `${NPM_TOKEN}` syntax (npm ≥ 7).

@mahirick:registry=https://npm.pkg.github.com
//npm.pkg.github.com/:_authToken=${NPM_TOKEN}
